#http://epicurious.com//recipes/food/views/Sliced-Baguette-with-Radishes-and-Anchovy-Butter-364610
IN	1/2 cup (1 stick) unsalted butter, room temperature
IN	2 to 3 anchovy fillets, finely chopped
IN	2 tablespoons chopped fresh chives
IN	Coarse kosher salt
IN	16 1/2-inch-thick diagonal slices baguette
IN	10 radishes (such as French Breakfast), trimmed, thinly sliced on diagonal
IN	Additional chopped fresh chives (for garnish)
PR	Mix butter, 2 chopped anchovy fillets, and 2 tablespoons chives in small bowl, adding 1 more chopped anchovy fillet to taste, if desired. Season with salt and freshly ground black pepper. Spread anchovy butter over 1 side of each baguette slice. Top each baguette slice with radish slices, overlapping slightly to cover bread. Garnish with additional chopped chives and serve.
